title: Ranked Team P1 / D5 +
body: Really wanting to be able to play consistent ranked 5's with** platinum 1 / Diamond 5 players**. If you can play during times of** 4 - 8 PM AEST / 6 - 10 PM NZT during weekdays**, and play more flexible time during weekends so that we may practice and participate in **online tournaments** then I want you. Must have working mike and can use **Skype / Teamspeak 3** then should be good. **First in first serve**, looking for players who main their roles i'll most likely go support. Add me in game "**Commando**" i'll get 5's going quite quickly see how it goes.
